title: Beautiful Card Component
html:
Product Feature

This is an amazing feature that will revolutionize your workflow.
css: .card { background: white; border-radius: 12px; box-shadow: 0 4px 6px rgba(0,0,0,0.1); padding: 0; overflow: hidden; max-width: 400px; margin: 20px auto; } .card-header { background: linear-gradient(135deg, #00d9ff, #8b5cf6); color: white; padding: 20px; } .card-header h3 { margin: 0; font-size: 1.5rem; } .card-body { padding: 20px; } .card-body p { color: #666; line-height: 1.6; margin-bottom: 20px; } .cta-button { background: linear-gradient(135deg, #00d9ff, #8b5cf6); color: white; border: none; padding: 12px 24px; border-radius: 6px; font-weight: bold; cursor: pointer; transition: transform 0.2s; } .cta-button:hover { transform: scale(1.05); }
